Let's go! Let's go!

15:45.740 --> 15:48.440
- Congratulations!
- Let's go!

15:48.440 --> 15:49.940
Let's go!

15:49.950 --> 15:51.410
Ready!

15:51.410 --> 15:52.380
Go, go, go!

15:55.330 --> 16:00.710
Congrats on getting into Tomei Univ!
The future depends on you!

15:55.880 --> 15:59.090
You got into the
prestigious Tomei University.

16:11.300 --> 16:13.600
I hardly did anything.

16:16.200 --> 16:18.200
You did it all by yourself.

16:19.010 --> 16:20.970
And then you left for Tokyo.

16:27.120 --> 16:27.950
Hey!

16:27.950 --> 16:28.850
- You!
- Hey.

16:32.890 --> 16:34.390
Hey.

16:34.390 --> 16:35.990
That's a tough book
you're reading.

16:34.450 --> 16:36.490
Being and Time by Heidegger

16:35.990 --> 16:39.160
It's not even one of the
books that's on the exam, is it?

16:39.160 --> 16:41.160
Yeah, I'm just
reading it for myself.

16:41.160 --> 16:42.760
Oh.

16:42.760 --> 16:44.800
Are you from the countryside?

16:44.800 --> 16:48.400
Listen, in
college, it's all about

16:48.400 --> 16:52.170
how well you use the notes
the past students left behind.

16:52.170 --> 16:53.240
Really?

16:53.240 --> 16:54.510
- Uh-huh.
- To land a good job,

16:54.510 --> 16:55.740
when you're outta here,
you got to be efficient.

16:55.740 --> 16:58.010
The more A's you get,
your chances are better

16:58.010 --> 16:59.410
of getting into a ministry.

17:01.350 --> 17:02.450
Hey, look!

17:02.450 --> 17:04.079
That's Chiaki Minase.

17:04.089 --> 17:07.450
