- Good morning.

17:10.230 --> 17:11.819
Man, she's hot.

17:21.900 --> 17:23.440
Chiaki Minase.

17:27.380 --> 17:29.480
I'll never
forget you, Satoru.

17:31.510 --> 17:34.010
