eventually become aware

17:34.020 --> 17:36.620
of your extraordinary
insight and genius.

17:40.350 --> 17:46.310
Become the wisest man in Japan!

17:46.290 --> 17:48.260
All right, here we go.

17:48.260 --> 17:49.530
I want to learn,

17:49.530 --> 17:52.530
and I want to use what
I learn for something.

17:52.530 --> 17:56.100
Those two passions carried
me all throughout my youth.

18:00.040 --> 18:01.740
Then one day...

18:03.850 --> 18:04.740
Yes?

18:10.890 --> 18:13.050
Mr. Ichijo, a telegram.

18:13.050 --> 18:14.220
Oh, thank you.

18:26.350 --> 18:30.020
Father in critical condition.
Come home ASAP.

18:29.840 --> 18:30.740
No.

18:36.480 --> 18:37.440
So how is he?

18:38.480 --> 18:40.950
Oh, he's fine, no worries.

18:40.950 --> 18:42.250
He'll be released

18:42.250 --> 18:44.050
from here soon.

18:44.050 --> 18:45.450
He's good. I see.

18:46.330 --> 18:48.330
Nobutada Ichijo

18:49.990 --> 18:50.890
How is he?

18:51.930 --> 18:54.890
He's got an acute
stomach ulcer.

18:54.900 --> 18:56.900
Luckily, we got here quickly,

18:56.900 --> 18:58.870
so they could save his life.

18:58.870 --> 19:01.400
But they told me that
he'll have to stay here

19:01.400 --> 19:02.870
for at least a whole month.

19:02.870 --> 19:04.100
Oh, really?

19:04.110 --> 19:05.710
Uh-huh.

19:05.710 --> 19:08.610
I'm glad he's alive.

19:12.680 --> 19:13.550
Father?

19:16.680 --> 19:19.790
Hey there, Satoru.

19:23.320 --> 19:24.390
Oh, Satoru.

19:26.490 --> 19:29.000
Mom must be relieved and
happy if you're around.

19:31.700 --> 19:34.400
