to look after Mom more,

19:34.400 --> 19:35.700
while I'm away.

19:35.700 --> 19:37.040
Your school's nearby.

19:37.970 --> 19:40.140
Oh, oh, yeah, sorry.

19:40.910 --> 19:41.810
Satoru.

19:45.250 --> 19:49.220
God forbid, if anything
happens to your father,

19:49.220 --> 19:51.380
I want you to know this.

19:51.390 --> 19:53.390
Don't worry about us.

19:53.390 --> 19:55.560
We'll be just fine, okay?

19:55.560 --> 19:58.220
