to get well for him.

20:55.850 --> 20:56.950
What are you reading?

20:57.820 --> 20:58.650
Max Weber.

20:58.650 --> 21:00.950
Oh, that's fantastic.

21:00.960 --> 21:02.490
That's a great
book to start with.

21:02.490 --> 21:03.590
- Your, uh-
- Yes.

21:03.590 --> 21:05.060
Future is bright.

21:06.190 --> 21:07.090
Thank you.

