a scholar or a politician.

21:23.850 --> 21:25.210
Yeah, but he's
the type who goes

21:25.210 --> 21:26.410
for what he thinks is right.

21:26.410 --> 21:27.910
Mm-hmm.

21:27.920 --> 21:30.020
In a way, he might be the
most successful of us all.

21:30.020 --> 21:31.480
Honestly, though,

21:31.490 --> 21:34.190
